nodes.text: Pisquatch's Place was a cantina located a few blocks down from Chalmun's on Outer Kerner Way, Mos Eisley on the planet Tatooine.

The Rebels Luke Skywalker and Leia Organa, along with Skywalker's Tatooine friends Windy Starkiller, Jaxson, Fixer and Camie Loneozner, once celebrated in the cantina to commemorate Skywalker and Jaxson's survival in the Jundland Wastes.
A garish painting of Noosh Feteel, one of Mos Eisley's founding fathers, was displayed in the cantina.
